ee an article from your hand in 6 to 12 months time stating you were wrong.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://yoast.com/seo-paul-boag/\">Want SEOs to lose their job? Start doing yours!</a> is a post by <a rel=\"author\" href=\"http://yoast.com/author/joost/\">Joost de Valk</a> on <a href=\"http://yoast.com\">Yoast - Tweaking Websites</a>. \n\nA good WordPress blog needs good hosting, you don\'t want your blog to be slow, or, even worse, down, do you? Check out my thoughts on <a href=\"http://yoast.com/wordpress-hosting/\">WordPress hosting</a>!</p><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/joostdevalk/~4/WWcHVnArg3s\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"/>\";}i:4;a:15:{s:5:\"title\";s:44:\"WordPress SEO, more secure than ever before.\";s:4:\"link\";s:58:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/joostdevalk/~3/JSZwFzQzmn4/\";s:8:\"comments\";s:59:\"http://yoast.com/wordpress-seo-sucuri-safe-plugin/#comments\";s:7:\"pubdate\";s:31:\"Fri, 07 Dec 2012 16:05:06 +0000\";s:2:\"dc\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";s:13:\"Joost de Valk\";}s:8:\"category\";s:39:\"WordPressWordPress PluginsWordPress SEO\";s:4:\"guid\";s:25:\"http://yoast.com/?p=60400\";s:11:\"description\";s:777:\"<p>One of the benefits of making money on paid plugins is that you can more easily spend money for other people to look at and even better, review your plugins. Today is the first result of what might become a somewhat longer tradition: WordPress SEO is now a Sucuri Safe Plugin. What this means? It&#8230;</p><p><a href=\"http://yoast.com/wordpress-seo-sucuri-safe-plugin/\">WordPress SEO, more secure than ever before.</a> is a post by <a rel=\"author\" href=\"http://yoast.com/author/joost/\">Joost de Valk</a> on <a href=\"http://yoast.com\">Yoast - Tweaking Websites</a>. \n\nA good WordPress blog needs good hosting, you don\'t want your blog to be slow, or, even worse, down, do you? Check out my thoughts on <a href=\"http://yoast.com/wordpress-hosting/\">WordPress hosting</a>!</p>\";s:7:\"content\";s:12:\"Array\n			\n		\";s:3:\"wfw\";a:1:{s:1